screen_desc: The screenshot shows a ride-hailing app interface with the title "Plan your ride." The user is prompted to enter a pickup point, with "VHC Health - Virginia Hospital Center" already selected. Below the input field, there are suggestions for pickup locations, including "VHC Health - Virginia Hospital Center" and "VHC Health - Cardiac Vascular & Thoracic." Additional options include "Search in a different city," "Get more results for VHC Health - Virginia," and "Set location on map." The time is displayed at the top left as 4:22 PM, and various status icons are visible at the top of the screen.
